So far. no casualties. but countries
everywhere are preparing for the worst.

769
01:07:54.989 --> 01:07:56.997
The gods are angry.

770
01:07:57.092 --> 01:08:00.554
We need to get the last pearl.
Where's the next location?

771
01:08:01.145 --> 01:08:03.592
Yeah. Let us see...

772
01:08:04.892 --> 01:08:08.071
Well guys. We got ourselves a good one.

773
01:08:08.166 --> 01:08:10.062
We're going to Vegas!

774
01:08:45.409 --> 01:08:47.097
There it is.

775
01:08:47.490 --> 01:08:49.536
Lotus Casino.

776
01:09:05.358 --> 01:09:07.454
I've been looking forward to this.

777
01:09:07.550 --> 01:09:10.372
Look guys. remember. always
put the 8's and never the 10's. okay.

778
01:09:10.468 --> 01:09:12.040
We're not here to gamble. remember?

779
01:09:12.137 --> 01:09:15.121
- They got poker. they got black jack.
- Grover.

780
01:09:15.217 --> 01:09:18.439
We're not here to have fun.
We just need to grab the pearl and go. okay.

781
01:09:21.825 --> 01:09:23.788
This is nice.

782
01:09:40.186 --> 01:09:42.029
This place is officially gold.

783
01:09:42.126 --> 01:09:44.163
Here is your complimentary
Lotus fun book.

784
01:09:44.259 --> 01:09:45.896
Thanks. but we're not staying.

785
01:09:45.992 --> 01:09:49.237
Please. I insist.
It's good for everything in the Hotel and Casino.

786
01:09:49.334 --> 01:09:51.916
Don't come to us.
We're not checking in.

787
01:09:52.170 --> 01:09:54.541
- That guy was persistent.
- Yeah.

788
01:09:55.729 --> 01:09:59.244
But we're here for one thing
and one thing only.

789
01:10:00.026 --> 01:10:02.242
That is really awesome.

790
01:10:04.144 --> 01:10:07.606
Where would we find a green
pearl in this place?

791
01:10:08.466 --> 01:10:12.307
Maybe I'll cap a waitress or a showgirl.
We should start there.

792
01:10:15.526 --> 01:10:17.132
Can I get you something?

793
01:10:17.229 --> 01:10:21.606
Try a Lotus flower. They're so good.
It's our signature dish.

794
01:10:22.348 --> 01:10:25.908
Really? Signature? Is it good?

795
01:10:26.803 --> 01:10:28.178
Thank you.

796
01:10:28.276 --> 01:10:30.294
Don't we have to pay for this?

797
01:10:30.391 --> 01:10:32.748
- I guess we don't.
- It's free.

798
01:10:35.988 --> 01:10:38.223
This is really good.

799
01:10:43.387 --> 01:10:46.363
This is the most delicious
thing I've ever consumed!

800
01:11:08.186 --> 01:11:10.595
Why don't we stay here for a while?

801
01:11:11.033 --> 01:11:12.913
That sounds like an amazing idea.

802
01:11:14.991 --> 01:11:19.983
But we're on a time sensitive
mission right now.

803
01:11:20.517 --> 01:11:22.290
Aren't we?

804
01:11:22.386 --> 01:11:24.040
I can't remember.

805
01:11:24.137 --> 01:11:26.805
I totally forgot what
I was gonna say.

806
01:11:26.902 --> 01:11:29.757
I think I figured it out.
I think I know why we're here.

807
01:11:29.853 --> 01:11:31.256
Why are we here?

808
01:11:31.352 --> 01:11:32.764
To have fun!

809
01:11:33.006 --> 01:11:37.711
Okay. Let's never leave.
Let's stay here!

810
01:12:16.617 --> 01:12:18.279
Awesome!

811
01:12:35.146 --> 01:12:38.434
No. Percy. don't
eat the flower.

812
01:12:39.191 --> 01:12:43.595
It dulls the senses.
It keeps you prisoner here.

813
01:12:44.223 --> 01:12:47.149
Hey. I'll get some air.
I'll be right back.

814
01:12:51.932 --> 01:12:55.287
- Another Lotus flower?
- No. I'm good. thank you.

815
01:12:58.047 --> 01:13:02.322
Look around you. Focus.

816
01:13:02.419 --> 01:13:04.785
- Lotus flower?
- No. thank you.

817
01:13:05.776 --> 01:13:08.207
- Would you like another one?
- I'm fine.

818
01:13:14.004 --> 01:13:18.239
- "The French Connection"?
- Yeah. you've seen it yet?

819
01:13:19.260 --> 01:13:21.669
Yeah. I think so. on DVD.

820
01:13:21.765 --> 01:13:23.763
What's DVD?

821
01:13:24.533 --> 01:13:26.516
Seriously?

822
01:13:26.613 --> 01:13:29.223
I think it's the best
movie of the year.

823
01:13:29.381 --> 01:13:32.429
What? Wait. this year?

824
01:13:33.612 --> 01:13:36.907
This year. 1971.

825
01:13:43.743 --> 01:13:45.418
Percy. wake up.

826
01:13:45.896 --> 01:13:48.302
You need to escape. Wake up!

827
01:13:48.399 --> 01:13:50.105
You can really use a Lotus flower.

828
01:13:50.203 --> 01:13:51.570
I really don't want that.
Thank you.

829
01:13:51.666 --> 01:13:53.614
- Just one.
- No.

830
01:14:07.799 --> 01:14:09.094
Another Lotus flower?

831
01:14:09.095 --> 01:14:10.703
- No.
- We insist.

832
01:14:10.703 --> 01:14:13.009
I really don't want another Lotus flower.
So please leave me alone.

833
01:14:13.010 --> 01:14:15.850
Is there a problem. Mr. Jackson?

834
01:14:16.667 --> 01:14:19.198
No. thank you.

835
01:14:24.084 --> 01:14:26.252
Percy Jackson is awake.

836
01:14:29.390 --> 01:14:31.004
Excuse me.

837
01:14:31.682 --> 01:14:32.987
What are you doing with that?
Don't eat that.

838
01:14:32.988 --> 01:14:34.294
- What?
- We have to go now.

839
01:14:34.392 --> 01:14:36.750
- What do you mean? We're having so much fun.
- No. we're not having fun.

840
01:14:36.847 --> 01:14:38.611
Grover. wake up!

841
01:14:38.708 --> 01:14:40.275
Grover. come one. we gotta go!

842
01:14:40.372 --> 01:14:43.169
Not now. Percy. your timing
is terrible. okay.

843
01:14:43.266 --> 01:14:46.070
Dude. we're heading to the chapel.
We're getting married.

844
01:14:46.167 --> 01:14:47.939
- How romantic!
- No. no. no ...

845
01:14:48.036 --> 01:14:50.497
Which one of you is going with me?

846
01:14:51.661 --> 01:14:53.247
Wake up!

847
01:14:53.344 --> 01:14:55.863
Yo man. you're such a bust kill!

848
01:14:55.960 --> 01:14:58.168
Percy. what's wrong with you?
Why are you doing this?

849
01:14:58.264 --> 01:14:59.922
Both of you need to wake up now!

850
01:15:00.018 --> 01:15:02.663
Look at me. you're in a trance. okay.
We're trapped!

851
01:15:02.760 --> 01:15:06.381
Listen to me. if you eat the flowers.
you'll never gonna leave.

852
01:15:06.591 --> 01:15:08.413
We're gonna be stuck here forever!

853
01:15:11.232 --> 01:15:13.088
Oh. no! We gotta go!

854
01:15:13.185 --> 01:15:14.885
Guys. we gotta go!

855
01:15:21.607 --> 01:15:23.743
Stop right there.

856
01:15:43.609 --> 01:15:45.152
Out of the way.

857
01:15:45.248 --> 01:15:46.833
Come on.

858
01:15:47.932 --> 01:15:49.714
Come on. guys. The car!

859
01:15:52.357 --> 01:15:55.363
Come on. come on. In the car.
Let's go. Keys.

860
01:15:55.651 --> 01:15:57.427
- I got the keys.
- Go. go!

861
01:15:57.548 --> 01:15:59.030
Incoming. Incoming.

862
01:15:59.126 --> 01:16:01.431
- I got this.
- Go!

863
01:16:22.715 --> 01:16:25.698
That's how you get out of a casino.
That's how you drive.

864
01:16:25.794 --> 01:16:28.447
- Of course. Now that all makes sense.
- What?

865
01:16:28.544 --> 01:16:30.416
That was the lair of the
"lotus-eaters."

866
01:16:30.514 --> 01:16:33.269
They've been luring people into
their traps since ancient times.

867
01:16:33.366 --> 01:16:35.991
Guys. look.
Tomorrow is June 21st.

868
01:16:36.088 --> 01:16:38.564
No. it can't be. Today is the 15th.

869
01:16:38.661 --> 01:16:42.141
No. Tomorrow is 21st. We were
in there for five days.

870
01:16:42.237 --> 01:16:45.108
- Felt like an hour.
- Tomorrow is the solstice.

871
01:16:45.206 --> 01:16:46.821
Our deadline is tomorrow
at midnight.

872
01:16:46.918 --> 01:16:49.313
Okay. look we gotta move.
Where's Hades?

873
01:16:55.840 --> 01:16:58.907
- He's in Hollywood.
- Alright.

874
01:16:58.908 --> 01:17:02.416
I can get us there in four hours.
Maybe three.

875
01:17:29.783 --> 01:17:32.604
And now the latest breaking news KZO1.

876
01:17:32.701 --> 01:17:34.736
An unprecedented storm cloud

877
01:17:34.832 --> 01:17:36.859
is swelling to cover most
of North America.

878
01:17:36.955 --> 01:17:39.589
Authorities in several states
are ordering evacuations

879
01:17:39.686 --> 01:17:42.475
and reporting severe
weather conditions.

880
01:17:48.715 --> 01:17:50.433
Watch your step.

881
01:17:51.607 --> 01:17:53.533
Wait.

882
01:17:59.015 --> 01:18:02.084
Woe to all depraved souls.

883
01:18:33.275 --> 01:18:36.202
- There's no turning back now.
- Yes.

884
01:18:36.308 --> 01:18:38.478
As if we're stuck in here.

885
01:18:48.452 --> 01:18:50.934
Percy. who's that creepy
guy with the hood?

886
01:18:51.030 --> 01:18:54.996
I don't know. Let's find out.

887
01:18:58.368 --> 01:19:01.613
- Who are you?
- We need to see Hades.

888
01:19:01.710 --> 01:19:06.927
The living are not permitted here.
Die and come back.

889
01:19:07.989 --> 01:19:11.739
Okay. we won't die
and come back...

890
01:19:11.883 --> 01:19:14.047
You know what?

891
01:19:16.707 --> 01:19:18.970
We gotta pay the ferry.

892
01:19:20.861 --> 01:19:23.944
Yo. my friend. What up?

893
01:19:25.252 --> 01:19:28.035
Okay. that's not like it.
You like dead. alright?

894
01:19:28.131 --> 01:19:30.799
I got here two dead people
you might recognize.

895
01:19:30.896 --> 01:19:34.882
Check this out: Jackson. Grant and
look who's joining the party.

896
01:19:35.154 --> 01:19:38.241
Benjamin Franklin.
Yeah. you like that. aren't you?

897
01:19:38.337 --> 01:19:42.021
You give us a boat ride. you take the money
and you get an interior decorator

898
01:19:42.118 --> 01:19:44.213
coz it's too depressing in here. alright.

899
01:19:44.310 --> 01:19:45.889
Here you go.

900
01:19:52.678 --> 01:19:55.766
- That's a $170.
- Wait.

901
01:19:56.401 --> 01:19:58.436
The Drachmas.

902
01:20:07.396 --> 01:20:08.761
Come aboard.

903
01:20:08.858 --> 01:20:11.286
Thanks for telling me. man.
You're burning money. we're in recession.

904
01:20:11.287 --> 01:20:13.815
- This is treason.
- Shut up.

905
01:20:31.855 --> 01:20:34.592
Welcome to the Underworld.

906
01:20:38.572 --> 01:20:40.831
What is all this?

907
01:20:42.176 --> 01:20:45.283
It's graphic of human misery.

908
01:20:45.380 --> 01:20:48.567
Lost hopes and dreams.

909
01:20:49.501 --> 01:20:52.645
Wishes that never came true.

910
01:21:05.624 --> 01:21:09.105
All lives end in
suffering and tragedy.

911
01:21:36.203 --> 01:21:38.573
This is as far as I go.

912
01:21:57.907 --> 01:21:59.465
Guys. do you hear that?

913
01:21:59.562 --> 01:22:01.756
- Yes. what is that?
- I don't know.

914
01:22:06.894 --> 01:22:09.664
What are we gonna do?

915
01:22:16.009 --> 01:22:19.040
- Who are those things?
- Hellhounds.

916
01:22:19.137 --> 01:22:22.077
Yeah. maybe you should feed them.

917
01:22:22.650 --> 01:22:25.755
They sense the presence
of another animal.

918
01:22:25.854 --> 01:22:28.963
- Great. I smell goat.
- You're a satyr.

919
01:22:31.909 --> 01:22:33.955
I haven't had a satyr...

920
01:22:36.031 --> 01:22:37.454
visit before.

921
01:22:37.549 --> 01:22:41.700
Persephone!
What would cause you to be taking so long?

922
01:22:41.796 --> 01:22:45.516
- Don't ignore me.
- Or what?

923
01:22:45.614 --> 01:22:50.011
What will you do? I'm already in hell.

924
01:23:08.529 --> 01:23:10.947
We have visitors.

925
01:23:13.426 --> 01:23:14.965
Well. that's you.

926
01:23:26.076 --> 01:23:27.797
Welcome.

927
01:23:29.059 --> 01:23:31.990
You have your father's looks.

928
01:23:32.245 --> 01:23:36.197
Always the lucky
side of the family.

929
01:23:37.000 --> 01:23:41.168
- Wait. You're Hades?
- Yes.

930
01:23:41.277 --> 01:23:45.161
I'm sorry. I just didn't expect
you to look like this. man.

931
01:23:45.259 --> 01:23:47.477
That was stylish. I like it.

932
01:23:47.574 --> 01:23:51.602
Would you prefer that I look like...this?

933
01:23:53.482 --> 01:23:57.252
No! Let's stick with
the Mick Jagger thing.

934
01:23:57.350 --> 01:23:59.268
It works for you.

935
01:24:07.322 --> 01:24:10.083
You're very brave coming here.

936
01:24:10.377 --> 01:24:12.367
Come closer.

937
01:24:15.743 --> 01:24:18.341
I can see a look of
disgust in your eyes.

938
01:24:18.439 --> 01:24:20.559
You see. disgust is
not righteous.

939
01:24:20.655 --> 01:24:23.324
I was banished here
by Zeus and his father.

940
01:24:23.460 --> 01:24:27.204
I'm done. My only chance
of getting out of this place...

941
01:24:27.302 --> 01:24:29.935
is defeat my brother and take
control of Olympus.

942
01:24:30.032 --> 01:24:33.535
Of course ... I need the bolt.

943
01:24:34.622 --> 01:24:36.330
And I need my mother.

944
01:24:36.426 --> 01:24:38.052
So we have an understanding.

945
01:24:38.149 --> 01:24:40.948
You give me the bolt and
I'll give you your mother.

946
01:24:45.206 --> 01:24:48.788
I need to tell you the truth.
I'm not the lightning thief.

947
01:24:48.885 --> 01:24:50.771
I don't have the bolt.

948
01:24:50.867 --> 01:24:52.906
I never did.

949
01:24:53.115 --> 01:24:55.986
Why did you come here then?

950
01:24:57.335 --> 01:24:59.537
Well. I was hoping that...

951
01:24:59.985 --> 01:25:03.458
when you saw that I wasn't the thief.
you'll let my mother go.

952
01:25:04.810 --> 01:25:07.001
Do you think I'm an idiot?

953
01:25:07.537 --> 01:25:12.983
I am Hades! Now give me the bolt
or say goodbye to your mother!

954
01:25:36.011 --> 01:25:37.787
Percy!

955
01:25:45.554 --> 01:25:47.482
I thought I lost you forever.

956
01:25:47.579 --> 01:25:48.984
No.

957
01:26:11.024 --> 01:26:14.123
Zeus' master bolt.

958
01:26:17.240 --> 01:26:18.864
Liar.

959
01:26:19.111 --> 01:26:20.490
I swear.

960
01:26:20.587 --> 01:26:23.127
I don't know how that got
into this. it's not even my shield.

961
01:26:23.224 --> 01:26:25.126
No. Luke rigged it.

962
01:26:25.222 --> 01:26:27.807
He put the bolt in your
shield and used us.

963
01:26:27.903 --> 01:26:29.542
Luke stole the lightning bolt.

964
01:26:29.639 --> 01:26:31.298
I think we're done here.

965
01:26:32.749 --> 01:26:34.906
Feed them to the souls.

966
01:26:48.812 --> 01:26:50.378
We had a deal. right?

967
01:26:50.474 --> 01:26:52.475
You have the bolt.
just let us go.

968
01:26:52.572 --> 01:26:54.295
Summon the hounds.

969
01:27:02.412 --> 01:27:04.438
Sit. sit.

970
01:27:10.059 --> 01:27:11.342
I...

971
01:27:11.439 --> 01:27:13.410
...am going to be king of the gods.

972
01:27:14.015 --> 01:27:15.504
Stay back!

973
01:27:17.370 --> 01:27:18.914
Stay!

974
01:27:26.928 --> 01:27:28.665
Alright. come on.

975
01:27:29.539 --> 01:27:31.290
Come on. give it back.

976
01:27:47.587 --> 01:27:49.241
Bad dog!

977
01:27:52.529 --> 01:27:55.029
He won't remember a thing.

978
01:27:56.129 --> 01:27:58.344
Why did you do that?

979
01:27:58.656 --> 01:28:00.295
Because...

980
01:28:00.670 --> 01:28:02.492
he's cruel and abusive.

981
01:28:03.346 --> 01:28:05.321
The only thing I look forward to

982
01:28:05.419 --> 01:28:07.683
is my allotted time
away from this hell hole.

983
01:28:07.780 --> 01:28:11.547
A war of the gods will put an end to that.

984
01:28:12.075 --> 01:28:14.064
And I'd be alone

985
01:28:14.161 --> 01:28:17.842
with only him forever.

986
01:28:19.958 --> 01:28:21.354
Go.

987
01:28:21.452 --> 01:28:23.568
Take the bolt and your mother.

988
01:28:33.733 --> 01:28:35.439
Only three?

989
01:28:37.279 --> 01:28:38.674
No.

990
01:28:38.772 --> 01:28:40.631
There are four of you.

991
01:28:40.996 --> 01:28:43.772
Each pearl transports
only a single person.

992
01:28:44.732 --> 01:28:46.823
One of you will have to stay.

993
01:28:47.339 --> 01:28:48.634
Alright. I'll stay.

994
01:28:48.731 --> 01:28:50.194
- You three go.
- What?

995
01:28:50.292 --> 01:28:52.838
- No.
- No. no. no. I've achieved my quest.

996
01:28:52.935 --> 01:28:55.335
- I'm staying here.
- I've trained for situations like this.

997
01:28:55.432 --> 01:28:57.333
Guys. guys. knock it off.

998
01:28:58.005 --> 01:29:01.352
- I'm staying because I'm your protector.
- Grover. come on.

999
01:29:01.449 --> 01:29:05.314
Look. man. I don't need to hear it.
Just go. It's my duty.

1000
01:29:06.277 --> 01:29:08.222
It's my memoir.

1001
01:29:08.370 --> 01:29:10.080
We'll come back for you.

1002
01:29:10.961 --> 01:29:14.286
I will take very good care of you.

1003
01:29:15.503 --> 01:29:17.217
All right. Now move it. guys.

1004
01:29:17.314 --> 01:29:20.335
You need to be stepping on the pearl and
concentrating on where you wanna go.

1005
01:29:20.432 --> 01:29:21.772
Take this.

1006
01:29:22.556 --> 01:29:24.125
To Olympus.

1007
01:30:21.717 --> 01:30:23.872
Hey. look.

1008
01:30:29.068 --> 01:30:32.067
Zeus and Poseidon are
preparing for battle.

1009
01:30:33.173 --> 01:30:35.761
No. this isn't the right place.
This isn't Olympus.

1010
01:30:35.857 --> 01:30:37.977
This is the Empire State Building.

1011
01:30:38.074 --> 01:30:40.750
Percy. the entrance to
the Olympus is there.

1012
01:30:40.848 --> 01:30:43.033
Well. it's ten minutes till
midnight. let's move.

1013
01:30:43.129 --> 01:30:45.333
Percy Jackson.

1014
01:30:51.457 --> 01:30:54.171
You weren't supposed to
make it out alive.

1015
01:30:55.128 --> 01:30:58.080
I can't let you take that
bolt to Olympus.

1016
01:30:58.771 --> 01:31:00.596
I'm the lightning thief.

1017
01:31:01.192 --> 01:31:03.843
You hid the bolt in my shield.
Why?

1018
01:31:03.940 --> 01:31:07.460
Well. when you said you were
going to the Underworld. it hit me.

1019
01:31:08.130 --> 01:31:11.279
That is the perfect opportunity
to get the bolt to Hades.

1020
01:31:11.376 --> 01:31:13.247
Why would you do that?

1021
01:31:13.345 --> 01:31:15.535
To bring Olympus
crumbling down.

1022
01:31:16.417 --> 01:31:18.035
Percy. let's go.

1023
01:31:18.589 --> 01:31:20.187
Let's go.

1024
01:31:20.651 --> 01:31:24.043
Well. it's too late. Because I'm
returning the bolt to Zeus. right now.

1025
01:31:24.140 --> 01:31:26.019
Not before midnight.

1026
01:31:59.011 --> 01:32:00.912
- Are you alright?
- Yeah.

1027
01:32:02.740 --> 01:32:05.685
Luke. why do you want
a war of the gods?

1028
01:32:06.260 --> 01:32:07.898
Control.

1029
01:32:08.829 --> 01:32:11.087
They've been in power for too long.

1030
01:32:11.582 --> 01:32:14.297
I say it's time for our
generation to take over.

1031
01:32:14.395 --> 01:32:16.876
Remold the world in our image.

1032
01:32:16.974 --> 01:32:20.464
- A world of new heroes.
- You're no hero.

1033
01:32:36.639 --> 01:32:38.775
- Annabeth. are you alright?
- Yeah

1034
01:32:40.113 --> 01:32:41.692
Stay here.

1035
01:34:40.898 --> 01:34:43.289
Maybe they were wrong.

1036
01:34:44.129 --> 01:34:46.759
Maybe you're no
son of Poseidon.

1037
01:36:10.208 --> 01:36:12.406
I think I am the
son of Poseidon.

1038
01:36:33.949 --> 01:36:38.176
He got the bolt.
Come on! We got two minutes.

1039
01:37:18.387 --> 01:37:20.054
Olympus.

1040
01:37:25.970 --> 01:37:29.292
Percy. I can't get through.
You gotta go.

1041
01:37:45.498 --> 01:37:47.561
Silence!

1042
01:37:59.393 --> 01:38:01.172
It's almost midnight.

1043
01:38:01.269 --> 01:38:04.351
This was predestined.
You wanted to get this badly.

1044
01:38:04.450 --> 01:38:06.648
You have only yourself to blame!

1045
01:38:06.745 --> 01:38:08.375
Please!

1046
01:38:08.473 --> 01:38:11.386
Let's be rational.
War is not the answer!

1047
01:38:14.164 --> 01:38:17.404
- Time has run out.
- Wait!

1048
01:38:17.501 --> 01:38:19.909
Wait! Wait!

1049
01:38:28.903 --> 01:38:31.183
My name is Percy Jackson and...

1050
01:38:31.773 --> 01:38:34.294
I think you might be looking for this.

1051
01:38:48.888 --> 01:38:52.055
Give me the bolt. lightning thief.

1052
01:39:03.522 --> 01:39:05.822
You are wise to
betray your father.

1053
01:39:05.919 --> 01:39:10.106
I didn't steal it. But I have
no connection to Poseidon.

1054
01:39:10.593 --> 01:39:15.299
So tell me. If you didn't
steal it. then who did?

1055
01:39:15.396 --> 01:39:18.781
Luke. son of Hermes.

1056
01:39:22.067 --> 01:39:24.031
You see. he was angry with you.

1057
01:39:24.128 --> 01:39:25.886
All of you.

1058
01:39:25.984 --> 01:39:29.114
He wanted you to
destroy yourselves.

1059
01:39:39.128 --> 01:39:41.271
You have done well.

1060
01:39:53.344 --> 01:39:55.726
Let there be peace!

1061
01:39:59.993 --> 01:40:03.208
- Hi. Mom.
- Annabeth.

1062
01:40:03.984 --> 01:40:06.231
I'm so proud of you.

1063
01:40:08.408 --> 01:40:10.312
Zeus.

1064
01:40:10.409 --> 01:40:15.697
I have a good friend.
He is a satyr named Grover.

1065
01:40:16.088 --> 01:40:17.926
He's my protector and...

1066
01:40:18.024 --> 01:40:22.319
the only reason why escaped the
Underworld is because he stayed behind.

1067
01:40:23.350 --> 01:40:26.616
And now you expect
me to bring him back.

1068
01:40:28.413 --> 01:40:30.292
Very well.

1069
01:40:32.813 --> 01:40:36.460
I believe this assembly's
business here is finished.

1070
01:40:37.750 --> 01:40:39.822
Brother. please.

1071
01:40:40.243 --> 01:40:42.031
I need to speak with him.

1072
01:40:45.107 --> 01:40:47.074
Just this once.

1073
01:40:58.437 --> 01:41:00.714
I'll meet you outside.

1074
01:41:10.106 --> 01:41:12.891
I'm not expecting you
to forgive me.

1075
01:41:14.059 --> 01:41:16.492
But I want you to
know that I'm grateful.

1076
01:41:16.589 --> 01:41:18.822
I didn't do it for you.

1077
01:41:19.231 --> 01:41:21.448
I did it to save mom.

1078
01:41:27.612 --> 01:41:29.684
Please.

1079
01:41:29.780 --> 01:41:31.655
I don't have much time.

1080
01:41:33.820 --> 01:41:37.645
How old was I when you left?

1081
01:41:37.742 --> 01:41:39.672
Seven months.

1082
01:41:40.957 --> 01:41:44.805
Look I didn't need
you there all the time.

1083
01:41:46.103 --> 01:41:48.962
I would've like to have
seen you just once.

1084
01:41:51.977 --> 01:41:54.098
Why didn't you ever come back?

1085
01:41:58.819 --> 01:42:00.893
I wanted to.

1086
01:42:02.344 --> 01:42:04.125
When I was with you
and your mother

1087
01:42:04.222 --> 01:42:07.602
I became less concerned
with my responsibilities.

1088
01:42:07.700 --> 01:42:09.996
I was becoming human.

1089
01:42:11.664 --> 01:42:16.073
- And that's a bad thing?
- To a god? Zeus thinks.

1090
01:42:16.170 --> 01:42:18.302
That's why he pass the law
preventing gods from...

1091
01:42:18.398 --> 01:42:20.805
ever having contact
with their children.

1092
01:42:22.325 --> 01:42:24.410
Only because of you?

1093
01:42:27.758 --> 01:42:29.856
But I was always with you.

1094
01:42:31.822 --> 01:42:35.320
Just because you didn't see me.
doesn't mean that I wasn't there.

1095
01:42:36.182 --> 01:42:39.211
When you're in trouble.
I tried to help.

1096
01:42:40.458 --> 01:42:42.766
I heard you.

1097
01:42:42.863 --> 01:42:45.862
I know I'm not the father
you've always wanted.

1098
01:42:45.960 --> 01:42:48.805
But if you'll ever need me.
I will be there for you.

1099
01:42:49.625 --> 01:42:53.956
In your thoughts.
And in your dreams.

1100
01:42:55.564 --> 01:43:00.236
I will stand by you. Percy.
Always.

1101
01:43:24.988 --> 01:43:27.346
You can come visit me. Anytime.

1102
01:43:27.444 --> 01:43:30.557
Just promise me that I don't have
to see that loser Gabe ever again.

1103
01:43:30.654 --> 01:43:35.730
I kicked him out. Yeah. he's gone.
He's out of our lives forever.

1104
01:43:36.709 --> 01:43:38.965
Finally.

1105
01:43:45.327 --> 01:43:47.760
- I'm gonna miss you.
- Me too.

1106
01:43:54.917 --> 01:43:56.575
Percy?

1107
01:43:57.499 --> 01:43:59.981
This is where you belong.

1108
01:44:15.169 --> 01:44:16.913
Percy. watch out!

1109
01:44:17.010 --> 01:44:19.146
You guys gonna kill the man
who saved the world? Great job!

1110
01:44:19.243 --> 01:44:21.854
All you guys take a
lunch break. Thank you.

1111
01:44:22.261 --> 01:44:24.810
So. the conquering hero
returns triumphant.

1112
01:44:24.906 --> 01:44:27.935
- Grover.
- Have you noticed anything
different about me?

1113
01:44:28.033 --> 01:44:29.369
No.

1114
01:44:29.621 --> 01:44:33.572
Are you sure?
Anything that's improved about me?

1115
01:44:34.189 --> 01:44:38.264
No. what? You've been working out?
You got a new cologne? You smell good.

1116
01:44:38.362 --> 01:44:40.316
Look. man. I got my horns!

1117
01:44:40.413 --> 01:44:42.910
I should've seen it the whole time.
Hey. look at that thing.

1118
01:44:43.006 --> 01:44:44.962
You got little horns in your head.
It's crazy.

1119
01:44:45.058 --> 01:44:46.514
Zeus came through.

1120
01:44:46.894 --> 01:44:48.942
I'm now a senior protector.
first class. baby.

1121
01:44:49.038 --> 01:44:52.740
- Congratulations. Definitely. you're one.
- Thank you. man.

1122
01:44:54.682 --> 01:44:58.051
Keep moving. Keep moving.
Don't lose interest.

1123
01:44:58.148 --> 01:45:01.707
One foot in front of the other and the
next thing you know you're running.

1124
01:45:03.712 --> 01:45:05.349
Percy.

1125
01:45:08.000 --> 01:45:11.655
You left the camp. and
disobeyed my orders.

1126
01:45:12.401 --> 01:45:15.989
- Yeah. about that ...
- Which is why ...

1127
01:45:16.914 --> 01:45:19.334
you're my favorite student.

1128
01:45:19.717 --> 01:45:23.122
You can receive all the training
in the world but ultimately

1129
01:45:23.219 --> 01:45:25.374
you have to follow your instincts.

1130
01:45:25.705 --> 01:45:27.530
Grace under pressure.

1131
01:45:30.703 --> 01:45:33.995
Alright. I'm trying to train.
Go suit up.

1132
01:45:34.091 --> 01:45:36.449
You might be a big shot on
Olympus. but down here

1133
01:45:36.546 --> 01:45:39.012
you're still just one of my students.

1134
01:45:39.109 --> 01:45:40.610
Move it.

1135
01:45:42.646 --> 01:45:44.371
Nice horns. Grover.

1136
01:45:44.468 --> 01:45:48.594
It's crazy. We talked.
We dined. We had a great time.

1137
01:45:48.690 --> 01:45:50.032
I'm happy for you. you know.

1138
01:45:50.129 --> 01:45:52.364
Persephone might really like me.
I'm serious.

1139
01:45:58.340 --> 01:46:01.160
You can handle this
one on your own. man.

1140
01:46:01.491 --> 01:46:03.474
Alright. Percy.

1141
01:46:06.106 --> 01:46:08.991
- Good job. Percy.
- Thank you.

1142
01:46:22.029 --> 01:46:23.809
Who's next?

1143
01:46:29.011 --> 01:46:31.385
I think I'd like to give it a shot.

1144
01:46:42.223 --> 01:46:44.440
Welcome home.

1145
01:46:49.988 --> 01:46:51.918
Whoa. whoa. wait!

1146
01:46:52.645 --> 01:46:55.035
First rule of battle strategy:

1147
01:46:55.132 --> 01:46:58.326
Don't ever let your
opponent distract you.
